response.original_title: Chikara Never Kneel At The Altar Of Conformity
response.overview: Friday, July 31st, 2009 :: Rayna VonTash faces her trainer, Daizee Haze in a ladies bout. Gen 1 Originals return in a very special attraction, when Dragonfly wrestles Rorschach! In the main event, Green Ant makes his official debut when The Colony meets The Order of the Neo Solar Temple for a 6-man tag match! Matches featured:  1. Rorschach vs Dragonfly  2. Daizee Haze vs Rayna VonTash  3. The UnStable vs Incoherence & Hydra  4. Tim Donst vs Claudio Castagnoli  5. The Roughnecks vs Cheech & Cloudy  6. Amasis vs Lince Dorado  7. F.I.S.T. vs Jigsaw & Mike Quackenbush  8. The Colony vs The Order of the Neo-Solar Temple
response.title: Chikara Never Kneel At The Altar Of Conformity
